Yandex Disk.name: F04a.01
Yandex Disk.description: Does the company publish data about the total number of pieces of content restricted for violating the company's rules?

Yandex Disk.name: F04a.02
Yandex Disk.description: Does the company publish data on the number of pieces of content restricted based on which rule was violated?

Yandex Disk.name: F04a.03
Yandex Disk.description: Does the company publish data on the number of pieces of content it restricted based on the format of content? (e.g. text, image, video, live video)?

Yandex Disk.name: F04a.04
Yandex Disk.description: Does the company publish data on the number of pieces of content it restricted based on the method used to identify the violation?

Yandex Disk.name: F04a.05
Yandex Disk.description: Does the company publish this data at least four times a year?

Yandex Disk.name: F04a.06
Yandex Disk.description: Can the data be exported as a structured data file?
